import React from 'react'
import { Text, Button, HStack, Box, Avatar, AvatarBadge } from '@chakra-ui/core'
import { MdBookmarkBorder, MdControlPoint } from 'react-icons/md'
import {BsClipboardData, BsBell} from 'react-icons/bs'

export const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Box borderBottom="1px solid rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.8)" fontSize="sm" color="rgba(38, 38, 38, 1)">
      <Box d="flex" justifyContent="space-between" flexWrap="nowrap" minW="992px" maxW="1200px" w="100%" mx="auto" px="20px" py="5px" bg="white">
        <HStack>
          <Text mr="4" cursor="pointer" _hover={{ textColor: 'rgba(34, 34, 34, 1)', fontWeight: 450}}>探索</Text>
          <Text mr="4" cursor="pointer" _hover={{ textColor: 'rgba(34, 34, 34, 1)', fontWeight: 450}}>题库</Text>
          <Text mr="4" cursor="pointer" _hover={{ textColor: 'rgba(34, 34, 34, 1)', fontWeight: 450}}>讨论</Text>
          <Text mr="4" cursor="pointer" _hover={{ textColor: 'rgba(34, 34, 34, 1)', fontWeight: 450}}>竞赛</Text>
          <Text cursor="pointer" _hover={{ textColor: 'rgba(34, 34, 34, 1)', fontWeight: 450}}>企业</Text>
        </HStack>
        <HStack>
          <Button size="sm" leftIcon={<MdBookmarkBorder />} colorScheme="teal" variant="outline">下载App</Button>
          <Button size="sm" leftIcon={<MdControlPoint />} colorScheme="yellow" variant="outline">Plus会员</Button>
          <BsClipboardData size={18} />
          <BsBell size={18} />
          <Avatar szie="md"><AvatarBadge boxSize="0.6em" bg="green.500" /></Avatar>
        </HStack>      
      </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}
